">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列下周允许阿联酋资助的人道主义援助通过海上进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</link><description>当地卫生官员称，海上航线的开通预计将导致国际社会对以色列在加沙的人道主义危机提出更多批评，由于以色列在援助物资转移方面设置困难，迄今为止已有 18 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</guid></item><item><title>尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕是一位真正的英雄，因为他没有在种族隔离的重压下呻吟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</link><description>以色列电影制片人在柏林电影节上的获奖感言似乎冒犯了《国土报》记者的敏感耳朵</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和甘茨勉强的政治婚姻显示出稳定的曙光</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</link><description>本尼·甘茨的美国之行可能羞辱了内塔尼亚胡，但并没有真正威胁到以色列的战时政府 ■ 总理决定允许斋月期间在阿克萨清真寺进行礼拜自由，这表明了政府极右翼势力的局限性</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准在约旦河西岸定居点建造3,476套住房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-approves-construction-of-3-476-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/0000018e-144f-d792-a7be-3cffd18d0000</link><description>一些单位得到了政府的批准，他们称之为对两周前发生的袭击事件的回应，那次袭击造成一名以色列人死亡、11 人受伤。估计显示，今年批准的约旦河西岸住房数量创上世纪九十年代《奥斯陆协议》以来的最高水平</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-approves-construction-of-3-476-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/0000018e-144f-d792-a7be-3cffd18d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的政党驳回了对梅龙灾难的调查结果，称其为“政治挑衅”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dismisses-probe-findings-into-meron-disaster-labels-it-political-provocation/0000018e-13f7-d7d3-abce-73ffca6d0000</link><description>在对 2021 年梅龙灾难进行调查后，拉皮德猛烈抨击了总理，称“如果内塔尼亚胡是一名普通公民，他今天就会因过失杀人罪被起诉并入狱”。 2021 年年度庆祝活动发生踩踏事件，45 名极端正统信徒丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dismisses-probe-findings-into-meron-disaster-labels-it-political-provocation/0000018e-13f7-d7d3-abce-73ffca6d0000</guid></item><item><title>复仇、无知和无能：以色列对加沙灾难性的人道主义援助政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/vengeance-ignorance-and-incompetence-israels-disastrous-aid-policy-for-gaza/0000018e-13f5-d8fb-abff-57ff1e2d0000</link><description>在战争期间的不同时期，当非以色列媒体已经报道加沙的“饥荒”时，以色列官员仍然将对加沙人的人道主义援助视为“哈马斯的生命线”。在过去的五个月里，以色列从未制定过明确的政策允许物资进入加沙地带</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/vengeance-ignorance-and-incompetence-israels-disastrous-aid-policy-for-gaza/0000018e-13f5-d8fb-abff-57ff1e2d0000</guid></item><item><title>他的书几乎在以色列被禁。但科勒姆·麦肯对巴以冲突仍抱有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/author-colum-mccann-wants-to-humanize-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bb173f0000</link><description>科勒姆·麦肯的小说《Apeirogon》讲述了失去亲人的以色列和巴勒斯坦父亲之间非凡的友谊，现已出版希伯来语版本。作者不确定这是否是一个时机不佳的情况，或者是以色列人阅读他的书的正确时机</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/author-colum-mccann-wants-to-humanize-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bb173f0000</guid></item><item><title>梅龙灾难：内塔尼亚胡“个人负责”，但不应被免职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-releases-final-report-on-meron-disaster/0000018e-12cd-df16-a58e-1fffe7ad0000</link><description>该国家委员会发现，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡知道或应该知道近三年前在以色列北部梅龙山举行的 Lag B&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动期间导致 45 人死亡的危险和风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-releases-final-report-on-meron-disaster/0000018e-12cd-df16-a58e-1fffe7ad0000</guid></item><item><title>美国在斋月前推动加沙停火，但辛瓦尔似乎支持升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/u-s-in-final-push-for-gaza-truce-before-ramadan-but-sinwar-seems-to-favor-escalation/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-397733dd0000</link><description>以色列国防官员怀疑哈马斯领导人希望暴力蔓延到耶路撒冷和约旦河西岸，并顽固地阻挠停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/u-s-in-final-push-for-gaza-truce-before-ramadan-but-sinwar-seems-to-favor-escalation/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-397733dd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生、13人受伤；哈马斯称谈判“濒临崩溃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-live/idf-hits-hezbollah-launch-sites-used-to-fire-rockets-anti-tank-missiles-at-kiryat-shmona/0000018e-1170-db19-abae-7dfa03270000</link><description>以色列在耶路撒冷持刀袭击中中度受伤 ■ 哈马斯向阿拉伯媒体透露：谈判濒临崩溃，以色列没有满足我们的主要要求 ■ 以色列军方称过去 24 小时内有三名士兵在加沙受伤 ■ 以色列内阁成员本尼·甘茨强调需要拉法行动参与美国谈判 ■ 以色列批准在约旦河西岸定居点建造 3,476 套住房</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-live/idf-hits-hezbollah-launch-sites-used-to-fire-rockets-anti-tank-missiles-at-kiryat-shmona/0000018e-1170-db19-abae-7dfa03270000</guid></item><item><title>脾气暴躁的以色列高级外交官罕见地赢得了公关胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-tramtrum-throwing-top-diplomat-snatched-defeat-from-the-jaws-of-a-rare-pr-victory/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-39774bd10000</link><description>外交部长卡茨决定召回以色列驻联合国特使——表面上是为了抗议安理会未能就 10 月 7 日的暴行举行讨论——这进一步证明他将政党政治置于任何其他考虑之上</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-tramtrum-throwing-top-diplomat-snatched-defeat-from-the-jaws-of-a-rare-pr-victory/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-39774bd10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管本格维尔提出要求，以色列不会在斋月期间对阿克萨清真寺的礼拜者施加新的限制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-impose-new-limits-on-worshippers-at-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018e-1006-d917-adce-fd0e271f0000</link><description>针对内塔尼亚胡的决定，国家安全部长本-格维尔指责称，“内塔尼亚胡和战时内阁认为10月7日没有发生任何事情。这一决定将以色列公民置于危险之中，并可能给哈马斯带来胜利的形象”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 19:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-impose-new-limits-on-worshippers-at-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018e-1006-d917-adce-fd0e271f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 151 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-151/0000018e-0fa4-db19-abae-7fae6d6c0000</link><description>布林肯：有机会立即停火，由哈马斯决定是否准备好参与停火 ■ 美国、约旦向加沙北部空投援助物资 ■ 世界卫生组织：加沙北部营养不良“特别严重” ■ 两枚火箭弹黎巴嫩袭击了以色列北部的建筑物 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列将在斋月期间“尽一切努力维护阿克萨清真寺的礼拜自由” ■ 战争结束 151 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-151/0000018e-0fa4-db19-abae-7fae6d6c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁间谍软件公司背后的前以色列情报官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-former-israeli-intel-officer-behind-spyware-firms/0000018e-0f97-d343-a9de-2ff7cf830000</link><description>美国财政部对 Intellexa 的以色列创始人实施制裁，原因是该公司开发和销售“用于针对包括美国政府官员、记者和研究人员在内的美国人的商业间谍软件技术”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-former-israeli-intel-officer-behind-spyware-firms/0000018e-0f97-d343-a9de-2ff7cf830000</guid></item><item><title>如何根据社交媒体帖子创建 10 月 7 日存档？四位以色列历史学家正在寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-do-you-create-an-october-7-archive-from-social-media-four-historians-are-finding-out/0000018e-0f5b-d203-a9ce-1ffb67440000</link><description>特拉维夫大学博士生的一个新项目旨在记录黑色星期六的证词以及民间社会随后的反应，以确保官方的国家叙述不是未来唯一可以讲述的叙述。随之而来的是许多独特的挑战</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-do-you-create-an-october-7-archive-from-social-media-four-historians-are-finding-out/0000018e-0f5b-d203-a9ce-1ffb67440000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡希望世界指责以色列的种族灭绝、种族隔离和种族清洗”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-05/ty-article-podcast/netanyahu-wants-the-world-to-accuse-israel-of-genocide-apartheid-and-ethnic-cleansing/0000018e-0f0f-d203-a9ce-1fbf16dc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 16:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-05/ty-article-podcast/netanyahu-wants-the-world-to-accuse-israel-of-genocide-apartheid-and-ethnic-cleansing/0000018e-0f0f-d203-a9ce-1fbf16dc0000</guid></item><item><title>这座与加沙接壤的以色列城市的孩子们在战争中返回学校，感到恐惧和焦虑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/still-afraid-children-of-this-israeli-city-bordering-gaza-return-to-school-amidst-war/0000018e-0efa-dc50-a7af-1efbf4390000</link><description>斯德洛特市的学校自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来首次于周日重新开放，但对许多学生来说，即使是一次无辜的谈话也会让人痛苦地想起创伤。一位母亲说：“我希望政府知道它正在做什么让我们回到这里”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 16:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/still-afraid-children-of-this-israeli-city-bordering-gaza-return-to-school-amidst-war/0000018e-0efa-dc50-a7af-1efbf4390000</guid></item></channel></rss>